Forecast¶





















In [ ]:



     


model_1_fit1.plot_predict()
plt.show()



     


















    
    



























In [ ]:



     


n = 5 # Max 5 days
fc, se, conf = model_1_fit1.forecast(n, alpha=0.05)
dates = pd.date_range(max(data_btc_filter.index) + timedelta(days = 1), periods=n)

forecast_data = pd.DataFrame({'date':dates, 'fc':fc, 'se':se, 'lower_series':conf[:, 0], 'upper_series': conf[:, 1]})
forecast_data.set_index('date', inplace=True)

fig, ax = plt.subplots()
data_btc_filter.Close.plot(ax=ax, color = color_line)

# Construct the forecasts
forecast_data.fc.plot(ax=ax, style='k--')
ax.fill_between(forecast_data.index, forecast_data['lower_series'], forecast_data['upper_series'], color='k', alpha=0.1)
plt.title('Forecast model of BTC-USD')
plt.show()
